    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="Can I change how the text of my novel is displayed (such as including links to reference materials)?" class="article-title">
          Can I change how the text of my novel is displayed (such as including links to reference materials)?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>You can enable/disable reference material links in the formatting section of the settings of your novel work.</p>
<p>■ What are reference material links?<br>Reference materials can be consulted by readers of a novel.<br>Terms that are entered as reference materials will become a link in the novel's text that will display the definition of a term when selected.</p>
<p>▶<a href="#h_01FM6G2FN0JXA54DHQ5HECJVEA" target="_self">On desktop</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FM6G2XSW3ACT9XW1BHPA31E7" target="_self">On mobile</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FM6G359WCY9X63VADSG8W385" target="_self">On the app</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM6G2FN0JXA54DHQ5HECJVEA">Desktop version</h3>
<p>You can enable/disable reference material links using the Aa menu in the bottom portion of the page.</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409330933401/03________________01.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409330933401/03________________01.png" alt="03________________01.png" width="531" height="622"></a></p>
<p>When enabled, links will display in your novel's text for terms entered as reference materials, letting readers check the definition.</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409330937113/03________________02.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409330937113/03________________02.png" alt="03________________02.png" width="550" height="425"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM6G2XSW3ACT9XW1BHPA31E7">On mobile</h3>
<p>You can enable/disable reference material links by clicking the ・・・ button in the upper portion of the novel page.</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409338756889/03______________01.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409338756889/03______________01.png" alt="03______________01.png" width="573" height="541"></a></p>
<p>Links will display as follows:</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409330957849/03______________02.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409330957849/03______________02.png" alt="03______________02.png" width="581" height="952"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM6G359WCY9X63VADSG8W385">On the app</h3>
<p>Currently, reference material links cannot be enabled or disabled on the app.</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

